EN: My salary this month is equivalent to 500,000 yen.

ZH: 我们买了100美元折合的外币。
EN: We bought foreign currency equivalent to 100 US dollars.

ZH: 一公斤苹果折合成斤的话大概是2斤。
EN: One kilogram of apples is approximately equivalent to 2 jin.

